stories.text:
I created Traddit a free Investment Focused Reddit Client, to help declutter market related Reddit posts, Follow Subreddits and Stocks, Reddit Stock Trends, Short Interest data, Earnings Calendar, News with Sentiment Analysis, Real-Time Stock Prices and a Memes Page! No Ads and no Login Required Features that will be added soon: Fed data, FTD data, Darkpool data, Google search trends, politician trades data, daily short volume, whale trades, stock filter tool, Economic and special events calendar as well as podcasts and YouTube videos. Traddit for Reddit is available to download on Android and iOS

iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/traddit-for-reddit/id1593956528

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bytmatic.traddit&hl=en_US&gl=US
